## Project Description    
The app provides a centralized platform where users can upload details of lost or found items , 
 browse listings, and communicate securely with item owners or finders.



## Inspiration behind the Project  
Traditional methods of reporting lost items are often inefficient,relying on notice boards
This app streamlines the process by providing a digital platform for managing lost-and-found reports.

